All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
ArriveEvent
ArriveEvent represents a new Event with a Customer that has just arrived.
Customer
Customer has an id and a arrival time.
CustomerComparator
CustomerComparator sorts customers based on ID.
DoneEvent
DoneEvent is a Event after Customer is served.
Event
An Event is an action that contains information required at that point in time.
EventComparator
EventComparator sorts based on time, type of event and customer id.
GreedyCustomer
Customer has an id and a arrival time.
HumanServer
HumanServer's job is to serve, reject, finish serving and store waiting customers.
LeaveEvent
LeaveEvent represents a Event with a Customer that is leaving.
Main
Main is the client who provides parameters of the simulation.
NormalCustomer
Customer has an id and a arrival time.
SelfCheckoutServer
SelfCheckoutServer's job is to serve, reject, finish serving customers.
SelfCheckoutServerManager
SelfCheckoutServerManager helps all SelfCheckoutServers manage their customer queue.
ServeEvent
ServeEvent represents a Customer that is being served.
Server
Server's job is to serve, reject, wait, finish serving customers.
ServerBack
ServerBack represents a new Event of a server returning back to service.
ServerRest
ServerBack represents a new Event of a server halting service temporarily.
Shop
Shop contains all the servers.
Simulator
Simulator handles a priority queue of events and updates the servers and queue based on the server's response.
Stats
Keeps track of statistics of simulator.
WaitEvent
WaitEvent represents a Event with a Customer that is waiting.
